<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Malevolent Revitalization Core -->
  <ApocritonMechResurrector.label>憎恶核心复苏仪</ApocritonMechResurrector.label>
  <!-- EN: The Malevolent Revitalization Core is a battlefield implant reverse-engineered from the Apocriton's resurrection ability, enabling users to efficiently revive nearby mechanoids. Although designed to block the Apocriton's psychic interference, its neural link subtly exposes users to the "Nefarious Drone," gradually altering their cognition under the influence of Malevolent Intelligence.\n\nThe implant inject Nano Cyber Serum to reset resurrection charges in the battlefield. It can be upgraded up to three times, significantly enhancing revival capabilities but increasing mental strain, risking cognitive decay and irreversible psychological damage. -->
  <ApocritonMechResurrector.description>“憎恶核心复苏仪” 是铁锈战争时期，由有机生命基于憎恶毒蜂复活能力所设计的一种机械复活植入物。\n\n虽然设计者在技术层面, 隔离了憎恶毒蜂等战时常见的广域心灵无人机的攻击，但由于装置直接连接大脑部神经，使用者会时常承受到“憎恶低语”的侵扰, 导致其思维逐渐被憎恶智能腐化, 对所有生物样貌的单位产生负面看法, 也对周围人的死漠不关心。\n\n注意事项： 此装置需通过纳米数据流体重置机械复活能力，可重复安装3次以增强和重置使用者的机械复苏能力。</ApocritonMechResurrector.description>
  <!-- EN: Implant {0_label} -->
  <ApocritonMechResurrector.comps.CompUsableImplant.useLabel>植入 {0_label}</ApocritonMechResurrector.comps.CompUsableImplant.useLabel>
  
</LanguageData>